    <h1 style="font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-style: italic;font-weight:bold;color:#451907">FAQ</h1>
</div>
<br />
<div style="width:850px;margin-left:100px">
<p >
<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">1) What is the overall flow for securing sponsorships on SponsorMyCamp like?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> You first register an account on SponsorMyCamp. Next, you will be prompted to add in your camp details. After adding your camp details, you can proceed to the search page which will display the most relevant results according to your camp details. After selecting your desired sponsors, you can proceed to generate a sponsorship request to be sent to the sponsors. When you receive notifications from your desired sponsors who have accepted your request, you can then proceed to generate a contract to be sent out. The status window in the home page will be updated accordingly.</h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">2) What are the different sponsorship statuses in the home page?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> There are four main statuses which can be displayed, namely 1) Accepted (Sponsor has accepted your sponsorship request), 2) Rejected (Sponsor straightaway reject your request), 3) Cancelled (Sponsor has accepted but then cancelled your request), 4) Secured (Contract has been signed)</h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">3) What are the different sponsorship types?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> There are a few sponsorship types such as Monetary, Product-In-Kind, Prize, Food, Vouchers, Collaterals, Others.</h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">4) How do I find sponsors urgently?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> There is a urgent filter in the search page where you can utilize to customize the display listings to show sponsors who can accept urgent requests. </h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">5) What should I do if a sponsor cancels my camp?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> When a sponsor cancels your camps, the status window in the home page will update you let you choose the option of “find substitute”, which will direct you to the search page which will filter out urgent and relevant sponsors for you. Alternatively, you can head directly to the search page to look for alternative sponsors straightaway. </h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">6) How to delete a sponsor?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> In the status window on the home page, there is a rubbish bin icon for each sponsor. Clicking on this icon will prompt you to confirm whether you want to delete the sponsor.</h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">7) How to send a single sponsorship request?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> To send a single sponsorship request, just select your desired sponsor using the checkbox next to the sponsor’s name after completing the sponsorship request. </h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">8) How to send multiple sponsorship requests?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> To send multiple sponsorship requests, just select your desired multiple sponsors or click ‘All’ using the respective checkboxes after completing the sponsorship request.</h5>   
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">9) How do I save a sponsorship template according to type of sponsorship?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> On the ‘Send Sponsorship Request’ page, there is a ‘Save’ button where you can click to save the sponsorship template. The drop-down list on the left allows you to view previously saved templates. </h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">10) How do I send a contract?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> You can proceed to the Contract page to edit and send the contract to the sponsor. </h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">11) How do I save a request template?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> You can save and modify different request templates for various categories. The changes will be saved in the system, and you will be able to reuse the template the next time. </h5>    
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">12) How do I add a new camp?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> You can click on the “Manage/Switch Accounts” button on the top-right of your screen, which will display an add new camp button.  </h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">13) How to edit camp details?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> You can click on the “Manage/Switch Accounts” button on the top-right of your screen, which will display the individual camps with an “edit” option right beside. </h5>  
<br />

<h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:#4C2D21;font-family:American Typewriter, serif;font-size:x-large;font-style: italic">14) I have other questions about SponsorMyCamp. Who can I contact?</h4>
<h5 style="margin-left:15px;color:#263829;font-familty:Gill Sans, sans-serif;font-size:17px"><b>Ans:</b> You can send your enquiries to enquiries@sponsormycamp.io.</h5>  

</p>
